	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Famicom Titler and Famicom TV use the RGB PPU. A couple Famicom games, such as <em>Just Breed</em>, come with a warning on a package that they're not compatible with Famicom Titler or Famicom TV.

		

